<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Calendar exports now include notes</li>
      <li>Climate zone format tokens (z/zzzz) returning empty</li>
      <li>Festival condition summary not refreshing after note edits</li>
      <li>MiniCal timeskip ignoring increment changes on first skip</li>
      <li>PF1e rests advancing time during SBC statblock imports</li>
      <li>Scene config breaking on systems that extend it (Torg Eternity)</li>
      <li>STK import dropping events on wrong dates</li>
      <li>Weather preset name overrides missing from calendar exports</li>
      <li>Weather unit abbreviations (km/h, mm/h, in/h)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Improvements</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Macro-based Simple Timekeeping import with instructions panel</li>
      <li>Settings export "Include Notes" toggle removed; notes export with the calendar</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
